  <div>
  <ul>
    <li>Enter any string to search, or just click the Search button to see everything.</li>
    <li>Use Record Type to filter between Solution Write-ups, Data Science Concepts and Tools</li>
    <li>Click on the title of any search entry to see full details</li>
  </ul>
  </div>
